sentences.english: Mr. Rolston was born in the state of Virginia in 1932.
sentences.chinese: 羅爾斯頓先生1932年出生在弗吉尼亞。

sentences.english: In some years, April bursts upon Virginia hills in one prodigious leap ?

sentences.english: Katona applied early to the University of Virginia.

sentences.chinese: 四月不知怎的一躍，就來到了弗吉尼亞的小坡上。

sentences.english: Blue catfish were introduced into Virginia in 1974.

sentences.english: In the hour of danger, they have drawn no invidious distinctions between the sons of Virginia.

sentences.english: But by then, Lee and his men had crossed safely back into Virginia.

sentences.english: Status Offline Jonathan Haidt, psychologist, University of Virginia.

sentences.english: This election, Virginia, with 13 electoral votes is a tossup.

sentences.english: Pero ahora va a venir con nosortors en el coche de Virginia.
